    <item>
      <title>德国肖尔茨愿意讨论调整国家债务规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/germany-s-scholz-open-to-discuss-tweaking-country-s-debt-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨表示，他愿意讨论改革德国预算规则，该规则将借款限制在该国经济产出的一小部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/germany-s-scholz-open-to-discuss-tweaking-country-s-debt-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 18:48:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰遭遇大规模停电，俄罗斯袭击敖德萨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/russia-hits-odesa-as-ukraine-grapples-with-massive-power-outages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯军队在袭击乌克兰首都几小时后，就用弹道导弹瞄准了乌克兰南部，而敖德萨和哈尔科夫仍有近 50 万户家庭断电。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/russia-hits-odesa-as-ukraine-grapples-with-massive-power-outages</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 18:26:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
